                    How do I ask about FGM? Who should I ask?
                  </h3>
                  <p class="metadata">6 votes, 1 answer, 54 views</p>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/health-foundation/questions/what—are-the-signs-of-trafficking.html">
                  <h3 class="listing__title">
                    <img src="/health-foundation/assets/img/icon-discussion.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='/health-foundation/assets/img/icon-discussion.png'" aria-hidden="true" credit="Created by Vectors Market from the Noun Project" class="icon">

                    What are the signs of trafficking?
                  </h3>
                  <p class="metadata">6 votes, 1 answer, 54 views</p>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="/health-foundation/questions/is-everyone-entitled-to-free-secondary-care.html">
                  <h3 class="listing__title">
                    <img src="/health-foundation/assets/img/icon-discussion.svg" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='/health-foundation/assets/img/icon-discussion.png'" aria-hidden="true" credit="Created by Vectors Market from the Noun Project" class="icon">

                    Is everyone entitled to free secondary care?
                  </h3>
                  <p class="metadata">6 votes, 1 answer, 54 views</p>
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="ask-question">
              <h2 class="ask-question__title">
                Ask your own question
              </h2>
              <p class="ask-question__desc">
                Post your question to the community of interest
              </p>
              <a href="/health-foundation/questions/ask.html" class="btn btn-primary ask-question__btn">Ask a question</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
